Figure 5

Individual proteins from the data set in which distance is a strong predictor of rate but does not correlate with other structural metrics. (A) Correlations between different structural metrics and site-wise evolutionary rates. (B) Predicted site-wise evolutionary rates based on a generalized additive model. From top to bottom, structures are 1DHF, 1HKA, 1PJB, and 2ACY.
